          <div class="custom-card">
            <h2>Who iDeal started</h2>
            <p>
              iDeal was founded by Shikhil K.S. from Thrissur, driven by a vision to make premium Apple technology
              accessible and affordable for everyone. After recognizing the high demand for quality smartphones at
              reasonable prices, Shikhil decided to bridge this gap by offering pre-owned, top-quality iPhones. iDeal
              was
              born from the idea that everyone deserves an ideal balance of technology, quality, and affordability.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="custom-card">
            <h2>Things we take for granted</h2>
            <p>
              At iDeal, we often take for granted the power of accessible technology. We believe that a quality iPhone
              shouldn’t be a luxury but a realistic option for everyone. The reliability, ease of use, and customer
              experience we provide are elements we strive to perfect daily, making sure customers can enjoy the best
              without a second thought.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="custom-card">
            <h2>Future of iDeal</h2>
            <p>
              Our journey doesn’t stop with iPhones. iDeal aims to expand into a full marketplace of pre-owned Apple
              products, from iPads to MacBooks, while staying true to our core values of quality and affordability. We
              are
              committed to innovation, eco-friendly choices, and continuous improvement, setting new standards in the
              pre-owned tech industry.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="custom-card">
            <h2>Something nobody knows about us</h2>
            <p>
              Few people know that iDeal started as a small project and grew through community support and a deep-rooted
              belief in the value of accessible technology. Every device we sell goes through rigorous quality checks,
              often exceeding industry standards, all to make sure our customers get nothing short of excellence.
            </p>
          </div>

          <p class="quote">
            "Your ideal iPhone experience, without the premium price tag."
          </p>

          <div class="custom-card">
            <h2>Where do we stand now</h2>
            <p>
              Today, iDeal stands as a trusted platform where hundreds have found their ideal iPhone. We are continually
              growing, building a reputation for quality, reliability, and eco-friendliness, with customer satisfaction
              at
              the heart of everything we do. As we expand, we remain focused on delivering technology that empowers and
              connects people.
            </p>
